Yancheng. Yancheng.

11
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:34,900
I've liked you for so long.

12
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:36,159
I'm also a daughter of the Sheng family.

13
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:38,899
I can do everything that Sheng Mian can do.

14
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:42,920
What's the matter?

15
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,619
I'm not divorced yet.

16
00:01:44,619 --> 00:01:47,940
So eager to get into your brother-in-law's bed?

17
00:01:47,940 --> 00:01:49,059
Sheng Mian.

18
00:01:49,059 --> 00:01:50,619
Let me explain. I didn't know it was her.

19
00:01:50,619 --> 00:01:52,000
You don't need to explain.

20
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,680
I already know.

21
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:56,819
Sheng Mian, you did that on purpose.

22
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:13,460
Honey. Let's start over, okay?

23
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,620
Sure.

24
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,919
It's just a man.

25
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:22,779
Tomorrow, I'll take over as the president of Sheng Group.

26
00:02:22,779 --> 00:02:24,379
What kind of man can't I get?

27
00:02:24,379 --> 00:02:27,139
You're really impressive, Sister.

28
00:02:28,099 --> 00:02:31,259
I'll soon be calling you President Sheng.

29
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:36,140
Well then, I wish you all the best tomorrow, Sister.

30
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,139
Sheng Mian.

31
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:53,439
I know you were lying about starting over, but I don't care.

32
00:02:53,439 --> 00:02:56,680
I can wait until you truly forgive me.

33
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,559
You're drunk. Go to sleep.

34
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,499
Goodbye.

35
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:11,020
 Sheng Mian, I will win you back. 

36
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:17,679
Shareholders, we are deeply saddened by President Sheng's passing.

37
00:03:17,679 --> 00:03:20,760
But the company cannot be without leadership.

38
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:23,059
The document you have in hand

39
00:03:23,059 --> 00:03:28,659
is the agreement where Sheng Zhong transferred all his shares to Sheng Weiyuan.

40
00:03:28,659 --> 00:03:31,460
So, if there are no objections,

41
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:34,580
Sheng Weiyuan will take over as president.

42
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:36,219
Please trust me.

43
00:03:36,219 --> 00:03:39,520
As Sheng Zhong's daughter, I will fulfill my father's last wish

44
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,900
and contribute to Sheng Group's development.

45
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:43,839
Wait a minute.

46
00:03:46,339 --> 00:03:48,939
My dear sister. This is such an important meeting.

47
00:03:48,939 --> 00:03:51,560
How could you forget to invite me?

48
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:57,560
Sheng Mian, that's not your seat!

49
00:03:57,560 --> 00:04:00,860
Don't forget, your dad left no shares to you.

50
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:03,300
And you don't have any position in the company.

51
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:06,960
Don't interfere with our meeting.

52
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,379
Let me correct you.

53
00:04:08,379 --> 00:04:10,080
I'm not interfering.

54
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:12,719
I'm not like those who take crooked paths.

55
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:16,979
I walked in here openly, through the front door of the company.

56
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:22,659
Besides, I have some files here.

57
00:04:22,659 --> 00:04:26,940
Evidence of Auntie Su and Lawyer Wang tampering with my father's will.

58
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:28,759
Please take a look.

59
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,900
Sheng Mian, these are just baseless documents.

60
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:34,360
You can't prove the nonsense you're spouting.

61
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,900
You're too desperate to become the president.

62
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:38,620
Don't trust her!

63
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:41,700
Auntie Su, what a coincidence.

64
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:44,519
Not long ago, I ran into Lawyer Wang.

65
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:45,900
And he wanted me to tell you this.

66
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:49,200
He's been unable to sleep, thinking of you.

67
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,859
Sheng Mian, don't talk nonsense!

68
00:04:50,859 --> 00:04:53,340
Lawyer Wang and I are completely innocent!

69
00:04:53,979 --> 00:04:56,439
Everyone, don't-don't believe what she says

70
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:58,079
Innocent?

71
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,399
Ladies and gentlemen.

72
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:06,940
This is the recording of what happened in the hospital when my father was seriously ill.

73
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:09,859
Mrs. Su Lan and Lawyer Wang are caught on it.

74
00:05:09,859 --> 00:05:14,299
As for whether they're innocent, you can judge for yourselves.

75
00:05:14,299 --> 00:05:16,640
 He just fell into a coma. 

76
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:21,439
 That old devil actually left all his property to that little wretch, Sheng Mian. 

77
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,720
 We need to make our plans earlier. 

78
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,779
 Don't worry. I'm here. 

79
00:05:27,779 --> 00:05:32,339
 After Sheng Zhong dies, we won't have to keep our affair a secret anymore. 

80
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,279
Shareholders,

81
00:05:46,279 --> 00:05:50,179
this notarized document is the real asset transfer agreement signed by President Zhong before his death.

82
00:05:50,179 --> 00:05:52,339
I'm the biggest shareholder of Sheng Group.

83
00:05:52,339 --> 00:05:56,460
From now on, I'll take over the Sheng Group from my father.

84
00:06:02,379 --> 00:06:05,000
Mom! How could you do that with Lawyer Wang?

85
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,379
Did you ever care about Dad?

86
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:13,979
Daughter, it's all my fault.

87
00:06:13,979 --> 00:06:18,399
Shareholders, Sheng Weiyuan has been completely unaware of this matter from the beginning.

88
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:21,739
She's put a lot of effort into managing Sheng Group.

89
00:06:21,739 --> 00:06:25,700
I hope you won't look down on her because of me.

90
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,739
So what if you're the biggest shareholder?

91
00:06:27,739 --> 00:06:29,940
You've never worked a day at Sheng Group.

92
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:32,539
You aren't familiar with the company's affairs.

93
00:06:32,539 --> 00:06:35,099
Can everyone here trust you with the company?

94
00:06:35,099 --> 00:06:37,619
 Who says she's unfamiliar? 

95
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:16,219
Shareholders, I'm an investor of Sheng Group.

96
00:07:16,219 --> 00:07:19,879
I'm also president of Fu Group, Fu Yancheng.

97
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:22,820
Although Sheng Mian has never worked here,

98
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:27,260
she personally completed both of your financing documents.

99
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:32,959
Moreover, she has made a very precise analysis of the future development of the Sheng Group.

100
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:37,419
If it weren't for Su Lan's embezzlement of public funds, Sheng Group wouldn't be in this plight.

101
00:07:37,419 --> 00:07:41,760
I believe all of you are intelligent folks,

102
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:44,419
which is why you are shareholders.

103
00:07:44,419 --> 00:07:47,079
If all you do is blindly follow others

104
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:50,020
and are unwilling to trust Sheng Mian,

105
00:07:50,659 --> 00:07:52,920
I suggest you simply withdraw.

106
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:56,580
I'll immediately buy out any shareholder who wishes to leave.

107
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:07,460
According to company regulations, the president has a one-month probation period.

108
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:11,519
If the company's performance   does not increase by at least 20 percent over this time period,

109
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:13,600
the president must step down.

110
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,460
No problem.

111
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:17,839
You have no chance of winning against me.

112
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:22,359
If I fail during the month of probation, I'll take the blame and resign.

113
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:30,120
Anyway, thank you for helping me today.

114
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:34,579
Then can you give me a chance to treat you to dinner tonight?

115
00:08:34,579 --> 00:08:37,179
I've got so many things to tell you.

116
00:08:37,179 --> 00:08:39,020
There's a psychology clinic right next door.

117
