President Sheng, I'm here for an interview.

126
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:09,100
Wen Zhao.

127
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,159
What are you doing here?

128
00:09:12,159 --> 00:09:14,779
Sheng Mian, long time no see.

129
00:09:14,779 --> 00:09:16,200
Long time no see.

130
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,200
It's been so many years, but you're still the same as before.

131
