This is President Fu Yancheng of Fu Group.

134
00:09:33,059 --> 00:09:35,540
I'm also Sheng Mian's husband.

135
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,960
Hello, President Fu. I'm Sheng Mian's college classmate.

136
