 What's that? 

139
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:02,419
 Sheng Mian is about to take over Sheng Group. 

140
00:10:02,419 --> 00:10:06,240
 She needs an experienced professional manager. 

141
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:10,260
 You've been managing Fu Group's overseas business. 

142
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:13,539
 I'm well aware of your capabilities. 

143
00:10:13,539 --> 00:10:17,859
 So, I wanted you to come back and help Sheng Mian. 

144
