 President Fu, you know my relationship with Sheng Mian. 

145
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:23,819
 In addition, I've always had feelings for her. 

146
00:10:23,819 --> 00:10:25,459
 Aren't you afraid that... 

147
00:10:25,459 --> 00:10:30,380
 Sheng Mian is about to divorce Fu Yancheng. 

148
00:10:30,380 --> 00:10:32,939
 But I trust my judgment. 

149
00:10:32,939 --> 00:10:35,819
 These kids are destined to be together. 

150
00:10:35,819 --> 00:10:38,120
 They will never be separated. 

151
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:41,519
 As for how you handle things with Mian Mian, 

152
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:43,360
 that's a matter for you young people. 

153
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,379
 I won't interfere. 

154
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:47,960
 I understand what you're saying. 

155
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,900
 Do I still need to attend the company meeting this afternoon? 

156
00:10:49,900 --> 00:10:53,960
 After all these years, I've never even met the young President Fu. 

157
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:56,440
 You don't need to attend. 

158
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,840
 You're going to help Mian Mian. 

159
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:00,240
